{"word":"κενόω","slug":"κενόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰενόω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κενός\">κενός</a></el>] <b>make empty,</b> the idea of emptying things of their contents is extended <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ metaph.\">metaph.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> deprive of prestige/status <b><a href='B:570 2:7'>Phil 2:7</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> deprive of significance <b><a href='B:520 4:14'>Ro 4:14</a>; <a href='B:530 1:17'>1 Cor 1:17</a>; <a href='B:530 9:15'>9:15</a>; <a href='B:540 9:3'>2 Cor 9:3</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κενοφωνία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κέντρον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}